title: Wonderful apartment homes across the street from Evergreen State!
posting_body: ['We are a family-owned and operated apartment community that cares about our residents, their lives and providing a home where memories are created.', 'We want you here and it shows with our onsite professional property management and 24/7 emergency maintenance.', 'We pride ourselves in going the extra mile to take care of the beautiful community called Evergreen Rock Maple.', "Once you find us, you'll love it and then live a little better knowing you're being taken care of.", 'Enjoy these other offerings:', 'Free Parking', 'Beautifully Manicured Mature Landscape', 'On the Bus Line with Free Public Transit', 'Online Rent Payments', 'Open Balcony or Patio', 'Basketball Sports Court', 'Multiple Playgrounds', 'Outdoor Park Benches, Picnic Tables and BBQs', 'Cats welcome in our Evergreen Garden floor plans (max 2 w/ deposit)', 'Fitness Center', 'Wifi Lounge', 'Theater Room', 'Kitchen & Commons Area', 'Quick Access to Highway 101 and I-5', 'Qualifications: must have 650 or greater credit score (co-signers must be 750 or greater), must make 2.5x the stated rent (co-signer must make 4x the stated rent), no evictions in the past 7 years, no monies owed to other properties, no felonies in past 7 years, no open bankruptcies.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday 8am to 5pm', 'Saturday 9am to 4pm', 'Sunday By Appointment', 'Go to our website to check on availability <URL>', 'Check us out on social media @egrm.apts']
